snippet.title: Did you know that PIGS CAN BE SO FUNNY? - FUNNY PIG VIDEOS will make you DIE LAUGHING
snippet.description:
Pigs are awesome animals and super funny pets! They make us laugh super hard! This compilation is the most impossible try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look how all these pigs behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
